title: wow!
review: this is without a doubt, one of the greatest movies.  i've NEVER seen anything like it in my life.  i think that if a big movie production company woulda made it, it wouldn't be as good as it was with its low budgeting. it wasn't as scary as i thought it would be, but it was really cool

title: What a saucy Aussie
review: I LOVED THIS MOVIE....absolutely without a doubt the best so far.  Of course, this is considering I haven't seen Austin Powers 2 yet.  But I did love this film and that HOT aussie.  However what's that 10 Things poem? That was so the best poem ever!
